## Preamble

The purpose of this license is to ensure that the software it covers is not used for activities that violate fundamental human rights. The standards referenced in this license are drawn from international agreements and authorities on human rights norms, including the United Nations Universal Declaration of Human Rights, the International Covenant on Economic, Social and Cultural Rights, the International Covenant on Civil and Political Rights, and the International Labour Organization core conventions.

